cs.IT, cs.COMM, cs.NI, cs.SY, cs.MM

The paper discusses a novel transmission technique that combines OFDM-IM and MIMO, which are both related to communication and information theory (cs.IT) and network protocols (cs.COMM). The proposed scheme also involves multiple antennas and signal processing techniques (cs.NI, cs.SY), which are common topics in the field of wireless communication. Finally, the paper presents computer simulations to evaluate the performance of the proposed scheme (cs.MM).
